des:
HCIPL’s System is capable of all levels of control and automation. It is modular and can be scaled to automate any size real estate. Can be retrofit into an existing house, villa and or an apartment. Completely wireless so it is easy to upgrade. Most advanced features like Lighting control, Security, Comfort & Convenience, Energy Efficiency, and Entertainment control are readily addressed. 

After connecting Alexa to your SE products in a few simple steps: 
(1). Download our "SE" app in android or ios app market; 
(2). Register one SE account in our "SE" app; 
(3). You need to have some SE devices in hand; 
(4). Configure these devices in our " SE" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "SE" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market; 
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "SE" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category; 
(8). Click Enable skill of "SE", and you'll be navigated to SE login page; 
(9). Input your SE account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page; 
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these: 
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.” 
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.” 
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.” 
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green." 
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
